Package com.adobe.xmp.schema.service

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RelaxNGProvider
    Provides all available RelaxNG schema resources and referenced includes.
    SchemaCache
    Interface for a schema description cache.
    SchemaService
    Interface for a service to provide schema information for XMP schemas and properties.
    SchemaService.INamespaceCallback
    An interface to report prefix/namespace bindings during Relax NG parsing.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SchemaServiceFactory
    Factory to create instances of SchemaService
    StandardRelaxNGProvider
    The standard RelaxNG-provider provides access to standard Relax-NG resources present inside this bundle.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    SchemaServiceException
    Exception that indicates errors while retrieving schema or type information.
